# Frontend Rules — Omnix Runtime

Source: `packages/core/standards/frontend.md`

- TypeScript strict. No `any`.
- Tailwind + design tokens. No inline styles for non-trivial UI.
- shadcn/ui or Radix primitives. Do not reinvent.
- Server/client component split is intentional — not accidental.
- Every interactive element is keyboard-reachable and announces correctly.
- Test with Testing Library; query by role.
- Measure before optimizing.
- No layout shift: reserve space for images, async content, fonts.
